				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">On the map, area 3, the large area that is half covered by the colored box (with two pillars in the middle), is a great area to farm for xp. All the mobs are single pullable, and were pretty good xp at level 62. With a 58 necro friend and my shammy (57 at the time) we were completing the entire cycle with just enough time for the reset. At the far end (out of the colored box), a named spawns that drops some decent weapons--about one out of every three or four cycles. At 62 in that group I was getting a single blue (4%) per cycle, and about 8pp per kill.
<br />

<br />
It is very easy to invis to that spot and setup there, as there is plenty of space to work with away from mobs, and in the cavern there is only one wanderer that I saw the entire time. There are several named mobs that you can check on the way to the cavern, as well--all of which drops some nice melee items to sell.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=603792" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Unagia Donburi</a> -- Solusek Ro -- Gnome Arch Convoker of <a href="http://www.triadica.org/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Triadica</a>
